               <p>Q. Did you employ the prisoner to receive money for you - A. Yes; it was part of his duty. The money that he is charged with is the money he received from 
               <persName id="t18120916-192-person1531">
                  Jeremiah 
                  Pilcher
               <interp inst="t18120916-192-person1531" type="surname" value="Pilcher"></interp>
